{"tid":246070,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"報稅問題，父母免稅額","createTime":"2017-05-16T17:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T18:07:38.000Z","uid":9923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87755167d9706e5a63a7f463f6a7110fbe554f4b","tid":246070,"uid":9923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"1. 如你/你配偶 (非與你分開居住) 在本年度內供養父母／祖父母／外祖父母，你可以就每名受養父母／祖父母／外祖父母獲享供養父母／祖父母／外祖父母免稅額，要符合申請 免稅額資格，受供養父母／祖父母／外祖父母本年度必須︰ <br />\n- 通常在香港居住︰ <br />\n- 年齡已滿 55 歲 (2004/05課稅年度或以前，年齡為已滿 60 歲)，或有資格按政府傷殘津貼計劃申索津貼︰及 <br />\n- 至少連續 6 個月與你同住而無須付出十足費用︰或你／你配偶每年付出不少於 <br />\n$12,000 的金錢用以供養該名父母／祖父母／外祖父母。 <br />\n<br />\n2. 如果受供養的父母／祖父母／外祖父母在本年度內全年連續與你同住而並無付出十足費用，你亦可享有供養父母／祖父母／外祖父母額外免稅額。 <br />\n<br />\nPoint 2有咩特別意思? &quot;全年連續同住&quot;同point1的至少連續6個月同住有咩分別? <br />\n同埋&quot;付出十足費用&quot;又即係點解? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0001d887717e4375623e9419ef31487624973899","tid":246070,"uid":9923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0367b396f997167b25dce7bcff597fe9a108f97","tid":246070,"uid":21862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T18:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n2. 如果受供養的父母／祖父母／外祖父母在本年度內全年連續與你同住而並無付出十足費用，你亦可享有供養父母／祖父母／外祖父母<span style=\"color: red;\">額外</span>免稅額。 <br />\n<br />\nPoint 2有咩特別意思? &quot;全年連續同住&quot;同point1的至少連續6個月同住有咩分別? <br />\n同埋&quot;付出十足費用&quot;又即係點解? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/pdf/pam61c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2Fpam61c.pdf&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1d2839e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/pdf/pam61c.pdf</a><br />\nPart 1 嗰個條件免稅額係46000<br />\n如果你符合埋Part 2 total 係92000<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/ese/pa_comp_2016_17_budget/cpacfrm.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fese%2Fpa_comp_2016_17_budget%2Fcpacfrm.htm&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=956c15a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/ese/pa_comp_2016_17_budget/cpacfrm.htm</a><br />\n你可以用佢個計數機計下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}